Keep an A-Soul member as a pet in the browser, she can accompany you to read literature, watch videos, watch live broadcasts, and interact with you, collect corpus for you, and remind you to rest on time.
- Drag and drop: Xiaoran will follow the mouse to change the position and change the expression;
- Click: Xiaoran will change different expressions and pop up random preset sentences;
- Follow the mouse: Xiaoran will continue to follow the mouse position;
- Follow the click: Xiaoran will chase the position of the most recent mouse click;
Additional features:
- Drag and drop collection: Drag the link/picture/selected text to Xiaoran, and she will save it for you;
- Manage collections: Click the expand button to open/copy/delete collections in the pop-up page;

